# The `ObjectCache` Class Reference

<DoxygenPage pluginConfig={pluginConfig}>

This is the base <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/objectcache">ObjectCache</a> type which can be provided to an <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/executionengine">ExecutionEngine</a> for the purpose of avoiding compilation for Modules that have already been compiled and an object file is available. <a href="#details">More...</a>

## Description {#details}

This is the base <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/objectcache">ObjectCache</a> type which can be provided to an <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/executionengine">ExecutionEngine</a> for the purpose of avoiding compilation for Modules that have already been compiled and an object file is available.
